  <section class="field field-name-field-description field-type-text-with-summary field-label-hidden"><h2><strong>COVID-19 Resources</strong></h2>
<p><br><strong>Mass.gov</strong><br><a href="https://www.mass.gov/resource/information-on-the-outbreak-of-coronavirus-disease-2019-covid-19">https://www.mass.gov/resource/information-on-the-outbreak-of-coronavirus...</a><br><br><strong>CDC</strong><br><a href="https://www.cdc.gov/coronavirus/2019-nCoV/index.html">https://www.cdc.gov/coronavirus/2019-nCoV/index.html</a><br><br><strong>Mass Department of Elementary and Secondary Education</strong><br>(DESE): <a href="http://www.doe.mass.edu/sfs/emergencyplan/covid19.html%C2%A0">http://www.doe.mass.edu/sfs/emergencyplan/covid19.html </a><br><br><strong>Talking to Kids about COVID-19</strong><br><a href="https://www.pbs.org/parents/thrive/how-to-talk-to-your-kids-about-coronavirus">https://www.pbs.org/parents/thrive/how-to-talk-to-your-kids-about-corona...</a><br><a href="https://www.cdc.gov/coronavirus/2019-ncov/community/schools-childcare/talking-with-children.html">https://www.cdc.gov/coronavirus/2019-ncov/community/schools-childcare/ta...</a></p>
<p><strong>Technology Support</strong>: If you are trying to access school resources and have questions that require technical support, our technology department is here to help.  You can access tech support through your child's teacher or by sending an email to: <a href="mailto:techdept@wpsk12.org?subject=School%20Closure%20-%20Technical%20Support">techdept@wpsk12.org</a></p>
<p><strong>Curriculum Support</strong>: If you have questions about any of the Learn Anywhere assignments or need support with the curriculum contact your child's teacher or one of our curriculum coordinators and they can either help you or direct you to the right person: </p>
<p><a href="mailto:Social.Studies@wpsk12.org">Social.Studies@wpsk12.org</a><br><a href="mailto:Science@wpsk12.org">Science@wpsk12.org</a><br><a href="mailto:Math@wpsk12.org">Math@wpsk12.org</a><br><a href="mailto:World.Language@wpsk12.org%C2%A0">World.Language@wpsk12.org </a></p>  </section><!-- Staff and Member Tables --><!-- Custom Person Tables --><!-- BAC Import -->
